        public int evaluate(java.lang.Double val)
        Determine if the value should be assigned the selected grade.
        Parameters:
        val - value to be evaluated.
        Returns:
        0 if the value should be assigned the grade, >= 1 if the value should be assigned a grader higher than this one, or <= -1 if the value should be assigned a lower grade than this one.
